                            <li>Present different accountability approaches (progress tracking, social accountability, reward systems) (2 minutes)</li>
                            <li>Guide students in designing personalized systems (3 minutes)</li>
                            <li>Facilitate brief accountability partner matching (1 minute)</li>
                        </ol>
                        
                        <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-800 mb-1">Key Teaching Points:</h4>
                        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-2">
